{"word":"H8080 - שָׁמַן - shâman - shaw-man' - Become fat - கொழுத்த","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>שָׁמַן"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>shâman"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>shaw-man'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Become fat / கொழுத்த"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கொழு, கொழுத்துப்போ, கொழுத்ததாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to be (or become) fat, to grow fat"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) fat (substantive)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Hiphil) to make fat, to show fatness"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>shine</i>, that is, (by analogy) <i>be</i> (causatively <i>make</i>) <i>oily</i> or <i>gross: - </i>become (make, wax) fat."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4924 - מַשְׁמָן - mashmân - mash-mawn'/4924\">H4924</a>, <a href=\"#/H4925 - מִשְׁמַנָּה - Mishmannâh - mish-man-naw'/4925\">H4925</a>, <a href=\"#/H8080 - שָׁמַן - shâman - shaw-man'/8080\">H8080</a>, <a href=\"#/H8081 - שֶׁמֶן - shemen - sheh'-men/8081\">H8081</a>, <a href=\"#/H8082 - שָׁמֵן - shâmên - shaw-mane'/8082\">H8082</a>, <a href=\"#/H820 - אַשְׁמָן - ʼashmân - ash-mawn'/820\">H820</a>"}]}